t-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#BF360C;margin-bottom:4px;display:block;\">info</span>\n                        <h2 style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#F5ECEA;margin:0;line-height:1.2;\">The Shift Is Already Happening</h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:#D7CBC7;margin:0;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">Teams that adopted structure-first content in Q1 2026 are seeing 3x the reach of teams still designing first. The gap will only widen. This carousel is your wake-up call.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
