text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"800\">Architecture-led</text>\n            </g>\n            <text x=\"173\" y=\"183\" font-size=\"9px\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#D7CBC7\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.05em\">Emotional Architecture Score</text>\n            <text x=\"50\" y=\"14\" font-size=\"9px\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#D7CBC7\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0.05em\">Engagement Rate</text>\n        </svg></div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#D7CBC7;margin:0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">Scatter distribution illustrating the linear relationship between character mass and compile latency under concurrency tests.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
